      <title>据称丰田将在上海设立独资雷克萨斯工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/toyota-said-to-seek-wholly-owned-lexus-factory-in-shanghai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，丰田汽车公司正在与上海有关部门讨论建设一家独资工厂的可能性，但在这家日本汽车制造商在中国陷入困境之际，这将是一次冒险的举动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/toyota-said-to-seek-wholly-owned-lexus-factory-in-shanghai</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 09:28:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
